px; line-height: 26px; color: #424242; margin-bottom: 8px;\">비흡연자도 잠깐 쉴 수 있는 공간을 제공하고자 하는 아이디어에서 시작되었습니다.</li>\r\n          \r\n            <li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-left:17px; font-size:16px; line-height: 26px; color: #424242; margin-bottom: 8px;\">온라인 담타는 익명성과 휘발성을 이용해 자유로운 소셜 공간이 되었습니다.</li>\r\n          \r\n            <li style=\"text-align:justify; margin-left:17px; font-size:16px; line-height: 26px; color: #424242; margin-bottom: 8px;\">디자이너가 혼자서 이렇게 많은 유저를 끌어모을 수 있었던 비결은 무엇일까요?</li>\r\n          \r\n        </ul>\r\n        <a style=\"display: inline-flex; text-decoration: none !important;\"\r\n           href=\"https://u2525788.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=u001.pKjnA8YxT-2BGjeO00WuBcokrX3Mjvx4pPxetTgqgGq3UYEuvDx8mYkJB-2FTHEguSYvq7EfqUw-2FemN3sm-2FTmPnAWyLy561MSf-2F37uazpmzSi8bAvtncUfLgqFs-2FofMS0mNKCOIgXar-2Bw4hwSKEAtYOXjjwyttX0wM1QHLShEpKefzaTT2L8dkDbAiiJpTGJlprVQ7yW_L3TaM7BR0UAWeIeLVg7ivlWn6BAfzrcYaPrEEr1UBXGwt7uUBvYNoYShDCjUE-2BA2oBacgIGxKzjmMLsJRBVIZ1f76zX64nF3H9k55-2FzenFlaV-2F08loimzRcjL1MP2h3Z5WroEWO47CD9VMIHKrXzwp6eCesjjfWZ4fpWMJyKu-2BRPBG980uQwbECF1-2FfXVcXROaXHTsvWJBSNgXQWW3wua7hgEaSE-2BBD8SNXGGu7BAvAiwck6dwCpEmfyG7-2Bx4wRnSkrsM34Ypn6wqFR46vUYPw-3D-3D\">\r\n          <div style=\"margin-right: 6px; color:#6b16ee; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px;\">자세히 보기\r\n\r\n          </div>\r\n          <img style=\"width: 14px; height: 14px; margin-top: 6px;\"\r\n               src=\"https://media.wishket.com/images/email/yozmit/icon_menu_go@2x.png\"/>\r\n        </a>\r\n      </div>\r\n      \r\n        <div style=\"height: 1px; width: 100%; background-color: #eee; margin: 16px 0;\"></div>\r\n      \r\n  \r\n      <div style=\"padding: 40px 0;\">\r\n      <a class=\"image-thumbnail\" href=\"https://u2525788.ct.sendgrid.net/ls/click?upn=u001.pKjnA8YxT-2BGjeO00WuBcokrX3Mjvx4pPxetTgqgGq3UYEuvDx8mYkJB-2FTHEguSYv30VB7O5JO0x4WwhnuSwzZCp1R4TROF9Z2eKbH5anGxJ-2FNTP1EvNNLwme89xapO9ulIEnCQzAIs4HKqpPQMyuz-2BNObdNA-2Biq9hij5H5KrbyYBDjg8V